           JS it does a normal POST; the script adds an inline success state. -->
      <div class="contact" id="contact">
        <h2 class="contact__title">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="contact__sub">
          Questions, an integration, or a custom implementation needed? Send a
          message and we will get back to you.
